{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_92","type":"agent_message","text":"The first checked-in change fixed the original runtime class-definition failure, but the full `test` run exposed two follow-on runtime problems: the StAX provider class is no longer reachable under this open-world mode, and Native Image now wants `org.mozilla.javascript` preserved for interpreted dispatch. I’m validating the minimal additional native-image arguments before I make another edit, instead of stacking guesses into the build file."}}
